com.zenika.varnishtest

Interface OutputHandler


  • public interface OutputHandler
    This interface provides callback methods for varnishtest standard output and error handling. Methods are called line-by-line and it is the responsibility of the implementors to guarantee thread safety as different outputs might come from different threads.
    Author:
    Dridi Boukelmoune
